                .row
                  .col-xs-12
                    .section-content
                      h2
                        | Ready to Get Started?
                      p
                        | Lets make sure we’re the right fit before you continue:
                      ul.section-content-checklist
                        li.section-content-checklist-ele
                          label.form-field-label for="req1" Your digital assets is very important to your business
                        li.section-content-checklist-ele
                          label.form-field-label for="req2" Your business has a budget of at least $5,000
                        li.section-content-checklist-ele
                          label.form-field-label for="req3" Your business believes design is very important
                        li.section-content-checklist-ele
                          label.form-field-label for="req4" You know that your users is the key to your success
                        li.section-content-checklist-ele
                          label.form-field-label for="req5" You’re done with the Wordpress templates, the Squarespace’s, and you want to shake up your industry!
              .form-content.col-xs-12.col-md-4
                .row
                  .col-xs-12
                    p
                      | The rest is history. Supply your details.
                    .form-field
                      label.form-field-label for="name" Name
                      input.form-field-text type="text" name="name" id="name"
                    .form-field
                      label.form-field-label for="email" Email
                      input.form-field-text type="email" name="email" id="email"
                .row
                  .col-xs-12
                    p
                      | Now you’re ready to take action. What's up?
                    ul.section-content-checklist
                      li.section-content-checklist-ele
                        label.form-field-label for="service-website" 
                          input.form-field-checkbox type="checkbox" name="service[website]" id="service-website" value="Website"
                          | I need a website designed
                      li.section-content-checklist-ele
                        label.form-field-label for="service-app" 
                          input.form-field-checkbox type="checkbox" name="service[app]" id="service-app" value="App Design"
                          | I need an app designed
                      li.section-content-checklist-ele
                        label.form-field-label for="service-consulting" 
                          input.form-field-checkbox type="checkbox" name="service[consulting]" id="service-consulting" value="Design Consulting"
                          | I need Design Consulting
                      li.section-content-checklist-ele
                        label.form-field-label for="service-music" 
                          input.form-field-checkbox type="checkbox" name="service[music]" id="service-music" value="Music"
                          | Can I get some music?
                      li.section-content-checklist-ele
                        label.form-field-label for="service-general" 
                          input.form-field-checkbox type="checkbox" name="service[general]" id="service-general" value="General"
                          | Get something off my chest
